  "title": "Locum Aesthetic Doctor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lazz Aesthetic is a professional Aesthetic Medical Clinic. Our client is from mid to high end. Our commitment is to deliver scientifically proven evidence-based aesthetic and age management treatments with genuine care. Our employees are passionately committed to fundamentally change the future of medical aesthetic and age management care.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform medical-grade aesthetic treatments including injectables (Botox, skin boosters, fillers), Pico Laser, Helio laser treatments, chemical peels, and thread lifts to achieve optimal patient outcomes</li><li>Develop and recommend personalized patient treatment plans based on thorough assessment of patient concerns and clinical indications</li><li>Conduct detailed consultations to advise patients on treatment options and expected results, ensuring informed decision-making</li><li>Monitor and review patient progress against treatment plans, adjusting protocols to maximize efficacy and safety</li><li>Maintain consistently high standards of patient care and clinical hygiene in compliance with medical regulations</li><li>Manage patient enquiries by providing clear education about treatment courses and post-treatment care to enhance patient understanding and satisfaction</li><li>Train and mentor clinic staff on aesthetic procedures and patient care protocols to uphold clinical excellence</li><li>Foster a collaborative and respectful workplace environment that supports performance and shared mission delivery</li><li>Administer medical-grade chemical peels with precision and adherence to safety standards</li><li>Promote a friendly, warm, and exceptional patient experience to build trust and loyalty</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Medical degree: MBBS, MBChB, MBBCh, MD or equivalent</li><li>Registration as a medical doctor with the Singapore Medical Council</li><li>Attainment of all relevant Certificate of Competence (COCs) for aesthetic procedures</li></ul>",
